</section>

<section id="skills">
    <h2>Technical Skills</h2>

    <dl>
        <dt>HTML5</dt>
        <dd>Creating semantic and accessible web pages.</dd>

        <dt>Java</dt>
        <dd>Object-oriented programming and application development.</dd>

        <dt>Python</dt>
        <dd>Programming, scripting, and automation.</dd>

