            A semantic HTML5 portfolio website showcasing personal
            information, technical skills, projects, and contact details.
        </p>

        <p>
            Repository:
            <a href="https://github.com/yourusername/personal-portfolio">
                Personal Portfolio
            </a>
        </p>
